815
00:40:25,040 --> 00:40:27,010
They are the color of our lives.

816
00:40:27,010 --> 00:40:29,100
The beauty and the grace.

817
00:40:29,110 --> 00:40:31,010
I can see by
this gathering today,

818
00:40:31,010 --> 00:40:33,350
