819
00:40:33,350 --> 00:40:34,740
And so, little man,

820
00:40:34,750 --> 00:40:36,310
I wish you Godspeed.

821
00:40:36,310 --> 00:40:38,170
In front of all these
gathered on your behalf,

822
00:40:38,180 --> 00:40:42,710
I baptize you,
Owen Jeffrey Manning.

