825
00:41:09,010 --> 00:41:10,870
- Must've been a relief.

826
00:41:10,880 --> 00:41:13,780
- Jay, she was on a placebo.

827
00:41:14,750 --> 00:41:16,810
They never knew.

828
00:41:20,860 --> 00:41:24,660
It was all for nothing.

829
00:41:24,660 --> 00:41:27,790
- No, you cared.

830
00:41:27,800 --> 00:41:32,070
I think, if we care, then...

831
00:41:32,070 --> 00:41:35,710
whatever happens,
it's for something.

832
00:41:35,710 --> 00:41:40,180
We might not see the effect,
but...

833
00:41:40,180 --> 00:41:44,320
It goes out there
